This is right now.

42:57.199 --> 42:59.118
- How is this ever gonna work?
- Relax.

42:59.118 --> 43:00.786
I know how this plays out.

43:00.786 --> 43:02.788
I handle the wedding,
then I ping back home.

43:02.788 --> 43:05.457
Then junior pings back here,
and he handles the marriage.

43:05.541 --> 43:08.127
