- Well, technically, no.

43:13.173 --> 43:14.174
Well.

43:15.134 --> 43:17.344
What do you think, Dad?
Do I pass?

43:17.428 --> 43:19.847
Your mother would be proud.

43:22.099 --> 43:23.475
Well, that's all
that matters, right?

43:26.770 --> 43:27.813
You okay?

43:29.690 --> 43:30.816
