52:07.791 --> 52:09.251
Did I chase you away?

52:10.377 --> 52:14.631
- Well, uh, I...
- Come see me sometimes.

52:14.631 --> 52:17.509
- Excuse me?
- Well, if you time travel here,

52:17.509 --> 52:20.762
come see me.
You're my husband, I'm entitled.

52:22.138 --> 52:28.770
- Isn't that, uh... a bit...
- Henry, we're married.

52:33.692 --> 52:36.278
<i>I now pronounce
you man and wife.</i>

52:36.278 --> 52:38.196
You may now kiss the bride.

